  use any portion of this exhibit’s content are responsible for obtaining all necessary consent and/or 
  permissions as required by copyright law and bear sole responsibility for any infringing reuses.</p>
  <% if current_exhibit && show_contact_form? %>
   <p>
    For questions or more information, please use the <%= t('spotlight.header_links.contact') %> form at the top of the page.
    </p>
  <% end %>
</div>
<footer>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-10">
      <p><a href="https://www.library.cornell.edu/copyright">©<%= Time.zone.now.year %></a> Cornell University Library, Ithaca, NY 14853 | (607) 255-4144 | <a href="http://www.library.cornell.edu/privacy">Privacy</a> | <a href="https://www.library.cornell.edu/web-accessibility">Web Accessibility Assistance</a></p>
